
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Pricing";
	Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";

}

<div class="gtco-section">
	<div class="gtco-container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center gtco-heading animate-box">
				<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
				<p>Get answers to common questions about SRC Travel Agency's bus services, routes, and more.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
				<ul class="fh5co-faq-list">
					<li class="animate-box">
						<h2>What services does SRC Travel Agency offer?</h2>
						<p>SRC Travel Agency provides intercity and intracity bus services across major cities in Pakistan, ensuring comfort, safety, and timely departures.</p>
					</li>
					<li class="animate-box">
						<h2>Which routes are covered?</h2>
						<p>We cover popular routes such as Karachi to Lahore, Islamabad to Multan, and more. For a detailed list of routes, visit our website or contact customer support.</p>
					</li>
					<li class="animate-box">
						<h2>How do I book a ticket?</h2>
						<p>You can book tickets online through our website, mobile app, or at ticket counters located at bus terminals across Pakistan.</p>
					</li>
					<li class="animate-box">
						<h2>What is your baggage policy?</h2>
						<p>Each passenger is allowed a certain baggage limit depending on the type of service. Please refer to our baggage policy page for detailed information.</p>
					</li>
					<li class="animate-box">
						<h2>What should I do if I miss my bus?</h2>
						<p>If you miss your bus, please contact our customer service for assistance. Depending on availability, you may be accommodated on the next bus or offered alternative solutions.</p>
					</li>
					<li class="animate-box">
						<h2>Are there discounts available?</h2>
						<p>Yes, SRC Travel Agency offers discounts on advance bookings and for certain groups such as students and senior citizens. Check our promotions page for current offers.</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>



<div id="gtco-subscribe">
	<div class="gtco-container">
		<div class="row animate-box">
			<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center gtco-heading">
				<h2>Subscribe</h2>
				<p>Be the first to know about the new bus online service</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row animate-box">
			<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
				<form class="form-inline">
					<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="email" class="sr-only">Email</label>
							<input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Your Email">
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
						<button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-block">Subscribe</button>
					</div>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


